---
import Modal from "../components/Modal.astro";
---
<Modal modal_id="brokenechoes">
    <main slot="main">

        <h1>Broken Echoes</h1>

        <div style="margin: -40px 0 30px 5px; line-height: 175%;">
            <small class="tag" style="background-color: rgba(255,96,66,0.57); white-space: nowrap; margin: 0">Action/Adventure </small>
            &nbsp;
            <small class="tag" style="background-color: rgba(255,79,247,0.57); white-space: nowrap; margin: 0">PC </small>
            &nbsp;
            <small class="tag" style="background-color: rgba(111,239,88,0.57); white-space: nowrap; margin: 0">Indie </small>
            &nbsp;
        </div>

        <div class="bannervideo">
            <video style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="auto" controls autoplay muted loop preload="none">
                <source src="/brokenechoes/videos/brokenechoes_banner.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                Your browser does not support the video tag.
            </video>
        </div>

        <ol style="margin: 30px 2% 30px 2%; padding-right: 10px; font-size: 1em">
            <p>
                Broken Echoes is an independent project developed alongside my Master's colleagues. It's an action/adventure game with different combat classes, exploration and motion captured cinematics.
            </p>
        </ol>
        <ul>
            <li class="game-feature-list" style="list-style-type: '🖥️ ';">
                Took on the roles of Audio and UI Programmer, and Music Composer.
            </li>
            <li class="game-feature-list" style="list-style-type: '🎧 ';">
                Implemented dynamic SFX and ambience, adaptive music and 3D audio using the FMOD Studio middleware.
            </li>
            <li class="game-feature-list" style="list-style-type: '🎵 ';">
                Designed the game’s SFX and composed the game’s nine music tracks. 
                <br>Here's "The Broken Continuum", the battle theme.
                <br>
                <audio style="margin-top: 20px" controls>
                    <source src="/brokenechoes/audio/be_demo2.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
                    Your browser does not support the audio element.
                </audio>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <hr style="border: 1.5px solid #78c2ad; margin-top: 40px">

        <div class="button" style="margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 350%">
            <a href="https://ad-astra-studios.itch.io/broken-echoes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
               style="margin: 10px;">
                <button class="itchio-button"><nobr><img width="auto" height="28" alt="itchio_logo" style="outline: 0; transform: translateY(17%);" src="/stores/itchio.png"/>&nbsp itch.io</nobr></button>
            </a>
        </div>
        
    </main>
</Modal>